  Welcome to BlazzCore — a minimal, fast, Wayland-first Linux OS.

  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
  │  Desktop      Sway (Wayland compositor)                 │
  │  Audio        PipeWire + WirePlumber                    │
  │  Browser      Chromium (GPU-accelerated via VA-API)     │
  │  Shell        Bash                                      │
  │  Packages     pacman (Arch Linux)                       │
  │  Base         Arch Linux (rolling release)              │
  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

  Useful commands:
    blazzcore-browser   Launch Chromium with GPU acceleration
    blazzcore-settings  Settings (display, theme, wallpaper, sound)
    tictactoe           Play Tic Tac Toe
    nmtui               Connect to Wi-Fi
    pacman -Syu         Update all packages

  Shortcuts (Sway):
    Super + Enter       Open terminal (foot)
    Super + D           App launcher (wofi)
    Super + E           File manager (thunar)
    Super + V           Clipboard history
    Super + ,           Settings
    Super + Shift + Q   Close window
    Super + Shift + E   Exit Sway

